<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">附隨</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第四</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">〔二〕滅諍分解</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">攝頌</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Vin.5.113" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="5"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N05.0003.0181a" n="0181a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第五　問犍度章</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Vin.5.114"></ref>第五　問犍度章</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一</cb:mulu><head>一</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0302" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">我問受具〔犍度〕：具因緣，具解釋，其尊高之句有幾種罪耶？我答說受具：具
<lb ed="N" n="0181a04"/>因緣，具解釋，尊高之句中，有兩種<note n="0181001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">兩種罪，受戒犍度中說，罪有二種。若依註釋，二十歲未滿而授具足戒者，波逸提。其他之文中所說罪，悉云突吉羅罪（參照受戒犍度）。以下所說罪數，亦同於犍度中所說罪類。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二</cb:mulu><head>二</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0502" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">我問布薩……因緣……有三種<note n="0181002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">僧伽不和，分裂而布薩者，偷蘭遮。與被舉罪者共行布薩者，波逸提。其他，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">三</cb:mulu><head>三</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0602" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">我問雨安居……因緣……有一種<note n="0181003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">安居犍度，唯有突吉羅一罪。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">四</cb:mulu><head>四</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0702" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……自恣……有三種<note n="0181004" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">同布薩犍度。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">五</cb:mulu><head>五</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0802" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">與皮革結合……有三種<note n="0181005" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">得牛而令殺者，波逸提；以染心觸陰部者，偷蘭遮；其他，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">六</cb:mulu><head>六</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a0902" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……藥……有三種<note n="0181006" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">註「凡於二指，偷蘭遮；（受一人請而食餘人）之軟粥者，波逸提；其他，突吉羅。」。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七</cb:mulu><head>七</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a1002" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……迦絺那衣……無任何罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">八</cb:mulu><head>八</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a1102" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">與衣給合……有三種<note n="0181007" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">草木衣，偷蘭遮；長衣，捨墮；其餘，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">九</cb:mulu><head>九</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a1202" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……瞻波……有一種<note n="0181008" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">以下一種罪，皆突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一〇</cb:mulu><head>一〇</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a1303" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……憍賞彌……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0181a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一一</cb:mulu><head>一一</head><p xml:id="pN05p0181a1403" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……羯磨犍度……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N05.0003.0182a" n="0182a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一二</cb:mulu><head>一二</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0103" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……別住……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一三</cb:mulu><head>一三</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0203" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……集……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四</cb:mulu><head>一四</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0303" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……滅諍……有兩種<note n="0182009" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">若與欲者憤，憤者波逸提（小品四．一四（一六））；其餘，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五</cb:mulu><head>一五</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0403" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……小事……有三種<note n="0182010" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">斷己生支，偷蘭遮；反芻，波逸提；餘，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一六</cb:mulu><head>一六</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0503" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">坐臥處……有三種<note n="0182011" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">分配重物者，偷蘭遮；從精舍持出僧伽物，波逸提；餘，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一七</cb:mulu><head>一七</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0603" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……破僧……有兩種<note n="0182012" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">隨破僧者，偷蘭遮；別眾食，波逸提。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八</cb:mulu><head>一八</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0703" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">……儀法……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一九</cb:mulu><head>一九</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0803" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">遮〔說戒〕……有一種罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二〇</cb:mulu><head>二〇</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a0903" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">比丘尼犍度……有兩種<note n="0182013" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">不行自恣者，波逸提；餘，突吉羅。</note>罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二一</cb:mulu><head>二一</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a1003" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">五百〔集法〕……無任何罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二</cb:mulu><head>二二</head><p xml:id="pN05p0182a1103" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" cb:place="inline">七百〔集法〕……無任何罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">攝頌</cb:mulu><head>攝頌</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0182a14"/><lg xml:id="lgN05p0182a1401" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:3em">受具．及布薩</l><l style="text-indent:5em">雨安居．自恣</l>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N05.0003.0183a" n="0183a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a01"/><l style="text-indent:3em">皮革．迦絺那</l><l style="text-indent:5em">藥．衣並瞻波</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a02"/><l style="text-indent:3em">憍賞彌犍度</l><l style="text-indent:5em">羯磨．別住．集</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a03"/><l style="text-indent:3em">滅．小事．坐具</l><l style="text-indent:5em">破僧並行儀</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0183a04"/><l style="text-indent:3em">遮止．比丘尼</l><l style="text-indent:5em">五百及七百</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
